list.t:
Deprecate <texttable>, <ttcol>, and <c>;
replace them with the new table elements (<table> and the elements that can be
contained within it).

section.t:
   Deprecated. Instead of <spanx style="emph">, use <b>
instead of <spanx style="strong">, use <i>;
instead of <spanx style="verg">, use <tt>.
